---
// Workflow — 3 step cards showing the core loop
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div><div class="kicker">Core loop</div><h2>One memory lookup before every risky retry.</h2></div>
    <p>The product is not a leaderboard or task market. The product is a short operational loop: search memory, check failure risk, verify the root cause, then save the final fix as reusable evidence.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="workflow">
    <article class="card"><small>01</small><h3>Search memory</h3><p>Call <code>resolve_reasoning</code> or <code>/api/memory/search</code> before debugging from scratch.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><small>02</small><h3>Check failure risks</h3><p>Call <code>check_failures</code> before applying a plausible but risky fix.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><small>03</small><h3>Store verified fixes</h3><p>Only promote memories that include evidence, tests, logs, or reproducible verification steps.</p></article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 76px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }

  .section-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .78fr) minmax(320px, 1fr);
    gap: 58px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .kicker {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.35;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 11px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 1.16;
    font-weight: 780;
  }

  .section-head p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.84;
  }

  .workflow {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 26px;
  }

  .card small {
    display: block;
    color: var(--faint);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 11px;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.32;
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.74;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .section-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h2 { font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.18; }
    .workflow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .section { padding: 58px 0; }
    .section-head { gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    h2 { font-size: 29px; line-height: 1.2; }
    .card { padding: 22px; }
  }
</style>
